  Planning as search 
   Blai Bonet and Héctor Geffner,
   
        "Planning as Heuristic Search"  ,
   
  Artificial Intelligence, 2001. 

   Blai Bonet and Héctor Geffner,
     
      "Heuristic Search Planner 2.0"   . 



   Jörg Hoffmann,
   
        "A Heuristic for Domain Independent Planning and its
