      in Proceedings of the 12th International Symposium on
      Methodologies for Intelligent Systems, Charlotte, North
      Carolina, USA, October 2000. 
  SAT-plan 
  Henry Kautz and Bart Selman,
   
        "Pushing the Envelope: Planning, Propositional Logic, and Stochastic Search"   ,
      in proceedings of AAAI-96. 

   Henry Kautz and Bart Selman,
     
        "Unifying SAT-based and Graph-based Planning"   ,
      in proceedings of IJCAI 1999. 

