  Probabilistic Planning 

  Stephen M. Majercik and Michael L. Littman,
     
        "Using Caching To Solve Larger Probabilistic Planning Problems"   ,
      in AAAI/IAAI 1998, pages 954-959. 

   Stephen M. Majercik,
            "Planning Under Uncertainty Via Stochastic Satisfiability"  ,
      In Proceedings of the Sixteenth National Conference on Artificial Intelligence, page 950, 1999. 

   Stephen M. Majercik and Michael L. Littman,
     
        "MAXPLAN: A New Approach To Probabilistic Planning"   ,
      In Proceedings of the Fourth International Conference on Artificial
      Intelligence Planning Systems, pages 86-93, 1998. 
